        Last week, we asked you to confirm your group’s membership by choosing a password. We think this might have slipped your mind. But don’t worry—it’s not too late!<br>
        Activate it now with just one click:
    </p>
    <a style="color: #102438;" class="button" href="{{ activationUrl }}">I choose a password</a>
